&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking to hire our top talent Full Stack developer &amp;nbsp;to help build and lead a state of the art product in the B2B Sales Tech Arena. You’ll work alongside our CTO, Yotam Sela, to build and shape our product&amp;nbsp; to help make Aligned the next big thing in Sales-Tech.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a young PLG startup that is very well funded, by top VCs, with very strong traction in a CRM scale market that is ready to be claimed. We’re moving fast and strategically, with great passion for sales-tech, having led top revenue teams ourselves for over 20 years combined.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Other than that, we are passionate about building a positive, diverse, and supportive culture — we look for people who are inventors, builders, learners, and team players. Most of all, we are big believers in hiring for the right attitude and potential, so if you feel you might be missing one of the qualifications, we still encourage you to apply and tell us why your skills and values could be an asset to us.&lt;/p&gt;
