&lt;li&gt;You are independent, versatile, and enthusiastic about taking on new challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are a team player, with great communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Tech Stack - React.JS / Next.JS, Node.JS, Redis, Mongo, AWS.&lt;/li&gt;
