&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tel Aviv / Hybrid&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Aligned is a customer-facing AI Deal Workspace (Digital Sales Room) that helps revenue teams manage deal complexity by moving the chaotic email-links-files back-and-forth into a single space where deals run. With AI Agents, sellers can enable champions to sell internally, access hidden stakeholders, track buying signals, and follow the company&#39;s playbook, all from one shared workspace. No login required for buyers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We serve 1,000+ paying customers and 1M+ buyers per month, tripled revenue last year, and are recognized by G2 as leaders in AI-driven Digital Sales Rooms. Companies like Deel, SimilarWeb, ServiceNow, and Intel use Aligned to shorten sales cycles by 30% and increase win rates by up to 100%.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re on a mission to lead the shift from Sales Enablement to Buyer Enablement, because sellers can&#39;t sell if buyers can&#39;t buy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here’s the full version together:&lt;/p&gt;
